OL,4,CWilliamson wants to scrap bubbles to
OL,5,Ckeep pupils in school
OL,6, Education Secretary Gavin Williamson
OL,7, says he wants the school "bubble"
OL,8, system in England removed as soon as
OL,9, possible, as rising numbers of pupils
OL,10, are being sent home to isolate.
OL,12,FThis could happen alongside the next
OL,13,Fstep of the roadmap for unlocking the
OL,14,Fcountry from the pandemic, he told MPs.
OL,16,FBut Labour warned that schools needed
OL,17,Fimmediate action to avoid "chaos" in
OL,18,Fthe last weeks of term.
OL,20,FOfficial figures this week showed over
OL,21,F375,000 children have been sent home.
